com.guidewire.ab.external.entity

Interface PendingContactChange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Editable, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity, Validatable, Versionable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PendingContactCreate, PendingContactUpdate
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface PendingContactChange
extends Editable, Validatable, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity
    This entity is the abstract base entity for storing information about contact change requests to ContactManager that will require approval in ContactManager before being applied. There are two subtypes included with ContactManager, PendingContactUpdate to handle update changes to an existing ABContact and PendingContactCreate to handle the creation of a new ABContact. Once a PendingContactChange has been processed by the system it is deleted from the database.
